287
00:16:29,319 --> 00:16:32,519
You're the one who hid the rose jam too, aren't you?

288
00:16:32,519 --> 00:16:34,419
Just as expected,

289
00:16:34,419 --> 00:16:37,619
Misuzu sent Yuka off to buy a new bottle of jam.

290
00:16:37,619 --> 00:16:41,719
Then, you jumped in front of Yuka's car.

291
00:16:52,219 --> 00:16:54,019
You people!

292
00:16:54,019 --> 00:16:56,319
What's the commotion about?

293
00:16:56,319 --> 00:16:58,019
Hey, that car?

294
00:16:58,019 --> 00:17:00,919
