00:17:10,719 --> 00:17:12,619
Is it true, sis?

298
00:17:12,619 --> 00:17:14,419
Did you kill Mother, Chiharu?

299
00:17:14,419 --> 00:17:16,419
Where's the proof?

300
00:17:16,419 --> 00:17:18,719
If you're going as far as to say so, Mr. Mouri,

301
00:17:18,719 --> 00:17:21,119
