302
00:17:21,119 --> 00:17:23,119
The proof.

303
00:17:23,119 --> 00:17:24,119
Yes.

304
00:17:24,119 --> 00:17:27,819
What we've heard till now are all assumptions.

305
00:17:27,819 --> 00:17:30,519
Just because I was the last one to leave the room,

306
00:17:30,519 --> 00:17:34,219
