307
00:17:34,219 --> 00:17:35,319
Ridiculous.

308
00:17:35,319 --> 00:17:36,819
Yuka?

309
00:17:36,819 --> 00:17:37,819
Yes?

310
00:17:38,819 --> 00:17:41,819
