311
00:17:41,819 --> 00:17:45,219
Yes, because Madam used to like it.

312
00:17:45,219 --> 00:17:47,319
How about in the other rooms?

313
00:17:47,319 --> 00:17:48,319
No.

314
00:17:48,319 --> 00:17:52,019
This is the only room that a lily was decorated in.

315
00:17:52,019 --> 00:17:56,019
Mr. Mouri, just what are you getting at?

316
00:17:56,019 --> 00:17:58,619
Of course about proof.

317
00:17:59,819 --> 00:18:01,019
In other words,

318
00:18:01,019 --> 00:18:04,719
I'm talking about the pollen of the lily

319
00:18:04,719 --> 00:18:07,019
