352
00:20:00,319 --> 00:20:02,319
"No, Miss Chiharu".

353
00:20:02,319 --> 00:20:05,519
Miss Chiharu, Miss Chiharu, Miss Chiharu...

354
00:20:09,919 --> 00:20:12,119
It was just last week.

355
00:20:13,619 --> 00:20:17,519
As for her, she has nothing to do with me.

356
00:20:17,519 --> 00:20:18,719
It's okay, don't worry about it.

357
00:20:18,719 --> 00:20:21,719
She's just a child of my husband's ex-wife.

358
00:20:23,119 --> 00:20:24,519
Yes, that's right.

359
00:20:24,519 --> 00:20:27,319
The only two children who are blood related with me,

360
00:20:27,319 --> 00:20:30,119
Misuzu Shirakwa are Saori and Kyosuke.

361
00:20:30,119 --> 00:20:35,119
I'm not going to give her a cent of inheritance either!

362
00:20:41,719 --> 00:20:43,819
Miss Chiharu.

363
00:20:43,819 --> 00:20:46,919
This is my personal opinion

364
00:20:46,919 --> 00:20:50,719
